title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Always a pleasure watching your videos, Mary!

I could get behind an AHS:Prison. I think if they did a shipwreck or at sea horror season they could get away with AHS:Vacation, because it's a "Typical American Tradition" to go on a vacation and fly off to a nice hot place. I want something unattached to a previous season!
I can’t wait for scream queens returning!!!!!!!!

Billy Eichner and Sarah did an interview with Andy Cohen on his show, a fan called in and asked about the next season and they said they BOTH know SOME information about Season 9 they just said they wouldn't share of course. SO that means they're both most likely involved
wait can we see a source to the contract being extended cuz I'm super excited and telling everybody
